Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
displaySpareCell(25.10)                                displaySpareCell(25.10)

Name
       displaySpareCell - Displays the results of placing the spare instances

Syntax
       displaySpareCell

       Displays  the  results of placing the spare instances. You must specify
       the spare cell types or spare instances before placing the design.

Parameters
       None

Examples
       The following set of commands displays all spare instances  defined  by
       the specifySpareGate command:

       specifySpareGate -cell ADDFXLT1T10

       place_design

        displaySpareCell

Related Information
              * place_design

              * specifySpareGate

